allidyrr Ride was a street found in the coastal town of Aithelar in Callidyrr on the Moonshae Isles in .
Callidyrr Ride was found in southwest Aithelar in between Finns Alley and Blackdorns Way. Aerynns Street branched from its midpoint to the northeast.
